# UX & journey audit suggestion

When you modify any of the following:

- **Routing**: `src/App.jsx`, `src/pages.config.js`
- **Navigation / zone**: `src/components/navigationConfig.jsx`, `src/components/navigation/navigationVisibility.js`
- **Guards**: `src/components/routing/RouteGuard.jsx`
- **Layout**: `src/Layout.jsx`, `src/components/layout/` (AppLayout, Navbar, PublicLayout, SidebarNav)
- **Pages**: `src/pages/**` (especially entry/exit points of user, barber, shop, admin journeys)

